variables.name: STATE_JOINING_BACKGROUND
variables.comment: Playback is buffering in the background for initial playback start

variables.name: STATE_JOINING_FOREGROUND
variables.comment: Playback is buffering in the foreground for initial playback start

variables.name: STATE_PAUSED
variables.comment: Playback is paused but ready to play

variables.name: STATE_BUFFERING
variables.comment: Playback is buffering to resume active playback.

variables.name: STATE_SUPPRESSED
variables.comment: Playback is suppressed (e.g. due to audio focus loss).

variables.name: STATE_SUPPRESSED_BUFFERING
variables.comment: * Playback is suppressed (e.g. due to audio focus loss) while buffering to resume a playback.

variables.name: STATE_ENDED
variables.comment: Playback has reached the end of the media.

variables.name: STATE_STOPPED
variables.comment: Playback is stopped and can be restarted.

variables.name: STATE_FAILED
variables.comment: Playback is stopped due a fatal error and can be retried.

variables.name: STATE_INTERRUPTED_BY_AD
variables.comment: Playback is interrupted by an ad.

variables.name: STATE_ABANDONED
variables.comment: Playback is abandoned before reaching the end of the media.
